{"tid":1550272,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問呢幾隻咩藥","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:20.000Z","uid":229585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd7bb912016d9dff941860f9b5e82242169bef9","tid":1550272,"uid":229585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojkT1AV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojkT1AV.jpg&h=f76d51dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PkT1AZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PkT1AZ.jpg&h=ec7bb0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsNnUV3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsNnUV3.jpg&h=7feff9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBromhexine 8mg<br />\ncetirzine 10mg<br />\ndextromethotphan 15mg<br />\n<br />\n唔肯定邊隻打邊隻"},{"pid":"6ecb8d1f1a1d882c97df43853ce7580cc4baed7a","tid":1550272,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21332635749aa666fe83be9c8035b4e048427212","tid":1550272,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我警告你班仆街！<br />\n<br />\n聽日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該幫手執！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企！<br />\n</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n第二樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「多里安」Dorian <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在美國造成最少4人死亡</span></span>，南、北卡州超過35萬戶停電。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=1780ab0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&h=d997d1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2019/09/05/b6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04/thumbnail/620x349/8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4/0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbsnews1.cbsistatic.com%2Fhub%2Fi%2Fr%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2Fb6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04%2Fthumbnail%2F620x349%2F8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4%2F0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg&h=6aa446ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國歌(快d聽熟！) 、揮<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國旗！！！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=d14bec60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"1192a85b18a7a02c4a4be5dc69bc82102945e977","tid":1550272,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"春藥"},{"pid":"5138fe95526ed88d60811c32fd2c9d82135c41a5","tid":1550272,"uid":229585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07b6e60b88f9b91d4d45fac17a9e10d956524c54","tid":1550272,"uid":226258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"順序岩"},{"pid":"bf6c365915f244fd429702c08eaf4b45d4d8025f","tid":1550272,"uid":229585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d814a242235c7e057028e21d174d932c16f341","tid":1